---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Story -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray mb-6">
          Vending, Reimagined
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Smart Vend NC is transforming how Triangle businesses think about workplace refreshments. We believe your employees and customers deserve better than stale chips and sugary sodas — that's why we stock our machines with nutritious options that actually taste great.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-light leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Our AI-powered machines track inventory in real-time, predict popular items, and alert our team before products run low. The result? Fully stocked machines with fresh products, every time.
        </p>

        <!-- Founder Quote -->
        <blockquote class="relative border-l-4 border-primary pl-6 py-2">
          <p class="text-gray italic leading-relaxed mb-3">
            "We started Smart Vend NC because we saw a gap in the market. Businesses wanted healthier options for their teams but couldn't find a vending partner who delivered. Now we serve locations across the Triangle with snacks people actually feel good about eating."
          </p>
          <cite class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray not-italic">— Ram, Founder & CEO</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-14">
          <div class="text-center bg-off-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-muted/10">
            <p class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-1" data-count="10">10+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-muted font-medium">Locations Served</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center bg-off-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-muted/10">
            <p class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-1" data-count="50">50+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-muted font-medium">Snack Varieties</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center bg-off-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-muted/10">
            <p class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-1">99.5%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-muted font-medium">Uptime Rate</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service Area -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-gray mb-3">Serving the Triangle</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-light text-sm mb-5">
            We proudly serve businesses throughout Wake County and the greater Triangle region.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <a href="/locations/raleigh" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-light text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Raleigh</a>
            <a href="/locations/durham" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-light text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Durham</a>
            <a href="/locations/cary" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-light text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Cary</a>
            <a href="/locations/chapel-hill" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-light text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Chapel Hill</a>
            <a href="/locations/apex" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-light text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Apex</a>
            <a href="/locations/morrisville" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-light text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Morrisville</a>
            <a href="/locations/holly-springs" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-light text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Holly Springs</a>
            <a href="/locations/wake-forest" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-light text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">Wake Forest</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
